document_data.name: Larynda Telenna
document_data.mainbody: '''Larynda Telenna''' was the high priestess of [[Kiaransalee]] in the [[Moondeep Sea|Vault of Gnashing Teeth]] beneath [[Vaasa]]. She was also the leader of Kiaransalee's cult across the entirety of [[Faerûn]].
document_data.History: In [[1337 DR]], Larynda Telenna brought with her a group of acolytes who aided her in constructing the [[Acropolis of Thanatos]] in the ruins of the city [[V'elddrinnsshar]]. Among those who resided with her in the [[Vault of Gnashing Teeth]] was the [[keening spirit]] [[Gurden Myrinn]].
